snippet.title: v6.0 Arrow of Novae Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is updating to v6.0 "Arrow of Novae"!
S-rank battlesuit Herrscher of Human: Ego debuts!
EX Chapter and summer event series to be released! Stay tuned!

Voice Artists:
Elysia: Marina Inoue
Pardofelis: Nozomi Yamamoto
